{"type":"message","id":"959976df","parentId":"a6285849","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:37:09.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So there's already a `persona-voice` on ClawHub — it's by Hei-MaoM, for Feishu/Lark bots, generates short responses with TTS. It's specific to a Chinese platform and not relevant to what Zach is building.\n\nThere's `open-persona` — \"Meta-skill for building and managing agent persona skill packs\" — this sounds closest to what Zach is thinking. It's NeilJo-GY's, updated recently (2026-03-22).\n\nThere's `personality-switcher` — by Robb1010, from February. Lets you create and switch between personalities with `/personality` and `/create-personality`. Persists across sessions.\n \n`open-persona` seems like the direct competitor here — it's literally a meta-skill for persona packs. I should dig into what it actually does.","thinkingSignature":"f9aa8bf62ad44b765f178f15ce75dbd9d5f1dacb96dae35ba79b40f496134f76"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4vpmi08yt1a8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect open-persona --files 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4vpmi08yt1a8_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub inspect personality-switcher --files 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22745,"output":238,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36489,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774240624098}}
