{"type":"message","id":"5dc49ffa","parentId":"5581de9d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:37:27.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So there's already a fairly mature `open-persona` (v0.19.1) which is a meta-skill for persona management, and `personality-switcher` (v0.1.3) which lets you create and switch between personas via commands. Both are active on ClawHub.\n\nThe differentiator Zach has is:\n1. The **signal-based trait propagation** — it's context-aware, not just a static persona\n2. **SPARK integration** — emotional engine that shifts personality based on conversation content\n3. **Structural voice** — actually rewriting the generation prompt, not just system prompt hacking\n\nThe existing stuff is mostly about switching between static personas. Zach's thing is dynamic, context-reactive personality. That's meaningfully different.","thinkingSignature":"320c02d140ef5bd569a2e0c0a8b8baa20f00c5774419cdc20785d0e522168055"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nFound it. Here's what's already on ClawHub:\n\n**`open-persona`** (NeilJo-GY, v0.19.1) — closest to what you're thinking. Meta-skill for building and managing persona packs. Has architecture docs, presets, evolution system. Looks fairly mature.\n\n**`personality-switcher`** (Robb1010, v0.1.3) — `/personality` command to switch between saved personas, `/create-personality` to design new ones. Persists across sessions, has rollback safeguards. Simpler than open-persona.\n\n**`persona-voice`** (Hei-MaoM) — Chinese market, Feishu/Lark bot integration, TTS voice output. Not relevant to your thing.\n\n**What they all have in common:** They're essentially static persona templates — you pick one, it loads a SOUL.md/IDENTITY.md, that's the personality. None of them do **context-reactive trait propagation** based on the conversation content. That's the gap in the market. What you've built — signal-based trait detection + SPARK emotional engine + hysteresis — is genuinely different from what's already there.\n\nThe differentiator isn't the persona presets. It's that the personality *responds to what you're saying*. If I were building a shop around this, that's the demo I'd lead with.\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24688,"output":433,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38627,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774240632679}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d36740a","parentId":"5dc49ffa","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:40:14.661Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Mon 2026-03-23 00:40 EDT] yeah lets try and do it. Maybe take a look at all of my projects and spin up a couple plans for the best ideas you can come up with. use spark if you can to really brainstorm hard and also search the openclaw hub for similar products to make sure the spot isnt already taken."}],"timestamp":1774240814656}}
{"type":"message","id":"57909d61","parentId":"9d36740a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:40:23.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach wants me to:\n1. Look at all his projects\n2. Brainstorm plans/ideas for a \"living agent shop\" selling personality setups\n3. Use SPARK to brainstorm hard\n4. Search ClawHub for similar products\n\nLet me first check what projects exist, then run SPARK brainstorming, then search ClawHub for competitive landscape.","thinkingSignature":"ed133be5d6c70a98fb44ad61c4ff36263f07e324268f93638ba3b8a61e00f6a6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kdn5jbwvzvhh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\dev\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kdn5jbwvzvhh_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kdn5jbwvzvhh_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"agent shop\" 2>&1 && echo \"---\" && clawhub search \"personality marketplace\" 2>&1 && echo \"---\" && clawhub search \"agent personality\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":227,"cacheRead":32858,"cacheWrite":5353,"totalTokens":38481,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774240814660}}
